<br><b>48. Why hollow circular shafts are preferred when compared to solid circular shafts?</b>
<br>
<br>&bull; The torque transmitted by the hollow shaft is greater than the solid shaft.
<br>&bull; For same material, length and given torque, the weight of the hollow shaft will be less compared to solid shaft. 
